title.Name: title
title.Value: Will Owen SCCA Majors High Planes Raceway

description.Name: description
description.Value: This is the rolling start and first lap of the second race of SCCA Majors at High Planes Raceway in Colorado.  I am starting second to national Formula Mazda champion Alan McCallum.  I chase him the entire race until another car explodes and spills oil everywhere.  The race is ended at 13/18 laps because of the mess on the track.  Unfortunately that took away my chance to make a move for the lead.
